metadata.name: FRONKS 🐸📈
metadata.description:
FROG + STONKS = FRONKS 

Pepe de' Medici's first ever 1/1 on Foundation. 🏆

Art & Memes are one in the same. Let's share laughter & buidl this culture togther! Much luv to my frog fam 💚

Only one other Pepe Medici 1/1 piece in existance, securely vaulted by the legendary @hafftka. You could be next to join me on the journey & secure your place in crypto art history! 🐸🥂
